Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:02:00.44,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:117064,120442}{\fad(1000,500)}Tonan Hospital{NOTE:都南病院}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.69,0:02:05.82,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:120692,125822}Accounting Division{NOTE:会計}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:04.27,Default,Accountant,0,0,0,,{TIME:121652,124279}You need to understand\Nthat we can't wait forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:06.78,Default,Accountant,0,0,0,,{TIME:124279,126782}The money for the last month…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.78,0:02:08.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:126782,128909}I'm not saying we won't pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:11.07,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:128909,131078}I'm just asking you to\Ngive us a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:18.58,Default,Accountant,0,0,0,,{TIME:133622,138585}Considering the situation you're in,\NI'll see what I can do regarding the deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:20.21,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:138585,140212}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.21,0:02:23.75,Default,Accountant,0,0,0,,{TIME:140212,143757}It's just that 200,000 yen\Nis a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:28.22,Default,Accountant,0,0,0,,{TIME:143757,148220}We can't afford to keep a patient who doesn't pay\Nwhile we lack room to receive others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:31.18,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:148220,151181}I understand. I will settle\Nthe debt as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.27,0:02:40.14,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:157271,160148}Oh? Speak of the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:44.40,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:160148,164403}I was just telling your dad\Nhow hard you work, Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:48.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:165153,168907}You're so kind, Kuma-san.\NYou always look after my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:51.86,Default,Mine Shinsuke,0,0,0,,{TIME:169533,171868}Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:56.74,Default,Mine Shinsuke,0,0,0,,{TIME:173161,176748}I'm sorry for dumping\Neverything on your shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:04.46,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:178333,184464}That's fine, don't worry about it.\NI'll be fine as long as you get better, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:06.59,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:184464,186592}Did you hear that, Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:11.22,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:186592,191221}You're one lucky guy\Nfor having such a great daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.22,0:03:13.39,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:191221,193390}Come on, you're\Nexaggerating again, Kuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:17.10,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:193390,197102}I'm not exaggerating at all.\NI'm just telling your dad how things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:19.98,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:197102,199980}An ordinary girl wouldn't be able\Nto handle things so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:25.56,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:199980,205569}You work so hard to get him the best treatment\Npossible without even a single complaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:28.78,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:205569,208780}If this is not a picture of an ideal\Ndaughter, I don't know what is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:31.90,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:210449,211908}By the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:36.99,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:214369,216997}Are you sure you're fine\Nwith the treatment costs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:39.04,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:216997,219041}They're so high, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:40.91,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:219041,220917}It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.91,0:03:42.50,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:220917,222502}I'm sure it'll work out somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:46.92,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:224087,226923}{\i1}No. I'll make it work out.
