Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:38.63,Default,Stuckup,0,0,0,,{TIME:390837,398637}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I'm tired of this,  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  let me grow up already  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:45.81,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:401973,405811}I'm supposed to be her number one fan,\Nand she didn't tell me anything about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:48.10,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:405811,408104}How am I going to cheer for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:51.19,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:408104,411191}Don't feel hurt, Kuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:55.73,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:411191,415737}She's the kind of girl who does things without\Nthinking twice, not to mention warning anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:59.49,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:416822,419491}In fact I think that's one\Nof Nozomi-chan's virtues.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:00.65,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:419491,420659}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:03.28,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:421117,423286}Now it's Sis' turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:04.66,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:423286,424663}Oh? Where, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:08.20,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:424830,428208}{\i1}The next challenger is 17 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:11.71,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:428208,431711}{\i1}I present you Mine Nozomi,\Nyoung and full of grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:15.09,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:431711,435090}{\i1}She'll sing "The Letter".\NThe stage is all yours. Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:22.93,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:438051,442931}I've been waiting for you, Nozomi-chan!\NI'm here watching over you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.93,0:07:25.85,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:442931,445851}Come on, Nozomi-chan\Nis singing. Hurry, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:28.18,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:445851,448186}It's fine. It's enough for me\Nto be able to hear her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:26.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:438552,446977}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I wanted to be with you until I die  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:死んでもあなたと 暮らしていたいと}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:35.36,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:446977,455360}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I've tried so hard until now  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:今日まで努めた この私だけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:44.11,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:455360,464119}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Let's release this little bird  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  that we had raised together  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:二人で育てた 小鳥を逃がし}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:55.38,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:464119,475380}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Let's burn this picture  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  that we had drawn together  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:二人で描いた この絵燃やしましょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:08:03.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:475380,483972}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I still don't know  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  where we went wrong  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:何が悪いのか 今もわからない}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:12.64,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:483972,492647}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I still don't know  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  whose fault it is  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:だれのせいなのか 今もわからない}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.64,0:08:23.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:492647,503909}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  A farewell letter  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  written in tears  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:涙で綴りかけた お別れの手紙}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:15.60,Default,Critic,0,0,0,,{TIME:494524,495609}A good interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:16.98,Default,Critic,0,0,0,,{TIME:495609,496985}She has great voice, I admit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:19.02,Default,Critic,0,0,0,,{TIME:496985,499029}Very good for an amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:21.99,Default,Critic,0,0,0,,{TIME:499029,501990}I can't find fault with anything.\NTen out of ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:27.37,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:503909,507370}Yamada · Mine{NOTE:山田 · 峰}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:30.54,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:507871,510540}She did it! Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:33.54,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:510540,513543}You heard, Mom? She's won!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:36.63,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:513543,516630}I'm happy for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:48.30,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:523219,528308}{\i1}With her outstanding singing skills, Nozomi\Nwon for the second, then for the third,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.30,0:08:52.14,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:528308,532145}{\i1}then for the fourth time,\Nqualifying for the final round.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:59.31,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:535649,539319}{\i1}Excellent, excellent!\NYou've finally made it to the fifth round.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:02.57,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:539319,542572}{\i1}One more round and you'll win\Nthe big prize. Do you feel confident?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:06.20,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:543323,546201}Miki, look who's on television.\NCan you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:09.62,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:547494,549621}I won't forgive her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:13.66,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:549621,553667}She's my assistant, she has no right to\Nparticipate in TV shows without my permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:20.00,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:554709,560006}I'm certain she wants to show off\Nthat she can sing better than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:25.51,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:560006,565512}Don't worry, Mom. We just need to make sure\Nthat she won't make it to the final round.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:30.64,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:566262,570642}There is only one thing that is more\Nimportant to Nozomi than music.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:35.98,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:572435,575981}You see, she's in love with\Na boy called Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:39.31,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:575981,579317}Fanni? Ah, that boxer\Nwho went to America?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:44.69,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:579317,584698}Yes. What if she learned that he\Nhas suddenly returned home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:47.49,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:584698,587492}If he asked to pick him up from\NHaneda Airport when the contest is on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.49,0:09:49.78,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:587492,589786}Miki, you can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:51.74,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:589786,591746}Things are getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:59.25,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:595208,599254}Hey, hey, hey, Nozomi-chan!\NToday is the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:04.13,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:599254,604134}Your number one fan is here\Nto make sure that you win today as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:06.72,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:604134,606720}Oh, if you're here for Sis,\Nshe's gone to the studio already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:08.93,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:606720,608930}Huh?! We were late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:11.01,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:608930,611016}Hey, Yume!\NWe'd better hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:12.43,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:611016,612434}Hurry where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:14.47,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:612434,614477}Are you stupid or what?\NThe studio, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:18.56,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:617105,618565}Easy-peasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:20.02,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:618565,620025}Kazuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:22.56,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:620025,622569}You can't trick people like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:27.36,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:622569,627365}But we all know how Kuma-san can be.\NI didn't want you to be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:30.57,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:627365,630577}Don't be silly. If I made it that far,\Nnothing can make me nervous anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:32.41,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:630577,632412}That's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:34.99,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:632412,634998}Yuki will be watching\Nyou all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:39.00,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:635749,639002}I'll be fine thanks to you, Yuki-chan.\NLeave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:42.00,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:639002,642005}TV "Channel"{NOTE:チャンネルTV}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:48.92,Default,Stuckup,0,0,0,,{TIME:645633,648928}Hey, you. What do you think\Nof that Kōda Miki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:49.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:648928,649971}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:52.34,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:649345,652348}{\fad(0,1500)}The Rising Star{NOTE:歌う新生}
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.09,0:10:54.35,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:651097,654350}{\fad(1500,0)}Debut Of A Little Bird{NOTE:どべない小鳥でデビュー}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:54.64,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:649971,654642}She's very gorgeous.\NShe's quickly climbing the stairs to stardom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:56.22,Default,Stuckup,0,0,0,,{TIME:654642,656227}Ha, don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:11:01.31,Default,Stuckup,0,0,0,,{TIME:656227,661316}She just uses her father's money to sell her image\Nbefore she even released her first disc.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.31,0:11:04.23,Default,Stuckup,0,0,0,,{TIME:661316,664235}By the way, how many times\Nhave you participated in this show?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:07.11,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:664235,667113}"How many times"?\NIt's my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:09.74,Default,Stuckup,0,0,0,,{TIME:667113,669741}Oh? You look so sure of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:13.78,Default,Stuckup,0,0,0,,{TIME:669741,673787}In my case, appearing in shows\Nlike this feels almost like a job now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:15.87,Default,Stuckup,0,0,0,,{TIME:673787,675872}Everyone does what they can,\Nand I collect prizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:20.62,Default,Stuckup,0,0,0,,{TIME:677457,680627}Wait, are you my challenger\Nin this season?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:25.38,Default,Stuckup,0,0,0,,{TIME:681544,685381}If you are, don't get your hopes up about that\N200,000 yen. You don't stand a chance against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.59,0:11:30.38,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:686591,690386}{\i1}Who do you think you are?\NI won't lose either to you, or to Miki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:36.43,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:690386,696434}{\i1}Miki-san, I'm a few steps behind you for now,\Nbut I will catch up with you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:40.06,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:698103,700063}You have one hour left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:42.85,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:700063,702857}Today we'll have a special guest,\NIshida Ayumi-san in the jury.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:45.56,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:702857,705568}Additionally, due to a sudden illness\NMr. Komori wasn't able to make it today,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:48.53,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:705568,708530}and will be substituted by\NMr. Egawa Isao, a composer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:49.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:708530,709906}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:54.57,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:712325,714577}{\i1}Mr. Egawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:56.28,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:714577,716287}{\i1}Mr. Egawa is in the jury…
Comment: 0,0:11:59.29,0:11:59.29,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:719290,719290}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:01.79,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:719999,721793}{\i1}What were you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:05.54,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:721793,725547}{\i1}As soon as I turned my back and went to Europe,\Nyou signed a contract with some gangsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:07.96,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:725547,727966}{\i1}You went on a tour\Nwithout a single word!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:11.01,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:727966,731010}{\i1}I won't teach someone who does\Nwhatever she pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:13.51,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:731010,733513}{\i1}– Get out! Get out!\N– Sir…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:16.55,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:733513,736558}{\i1}– Get out! Get out!\N– Mr. Egawa…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:18.30,Default,Receptionist,0,0,0,,{TIME:736558,738309}{\i1}Mine Nozomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:23.06,Default,Receptionist,0,0,0,,{TIME:739561,743064}{\i1}Mine Nozomi-san,\Nthere's a telegram for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:26.94,Default,Receptionist,0,0,0,,{TIME:743064,746943}{\i1}Please pick it up at the reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:28.19,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:747360,748194}Uhm…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:30.15,Default,Receptionist,0,0,0,,{TIME:748194,750155}Mine Nozomi-san, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:32.24,Default,Receptionist,0,0,0,,{TIME:750155,752240}Here. This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:32.78,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:752240,752782}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:39.95,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:757078,759956}"I want to meet up with you\Nat Haneda Airport at 2 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:41.79,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:759956,761791}I'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:43.20,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:761791,763209}– Fanni."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:45.04,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:763209,765044}"Fanni"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:46.21,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:765044,766212}Fanni…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:51.30,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:769090,771301}Fanni… Fanni's…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.34,0:12:54.34,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:772343,774345}Fanni's back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:55.26,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:774345,775263}Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:13:00.72,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:777265,780727}{\i1}I want to meet him so bad.\NI've waited for this day for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:04.52,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:780727,784522}{\i1}But if I go now, I can\Nsay goodbye to the prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.52,0:13:07.15,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:784522,787150}{\i1}The final round of\Nthe show starts at 2:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:09.56,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:787150,789569}{\i1}Fanni will be at the airport at 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.53,0:13:20.07,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:795533,800079}{\i1}But if I pass that up, there's no knowing\Nwhen I get to meet him next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:22.70,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:800079,802707}{\i1}Ah, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:45.06,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:820266,825063}If Nozomi really shows up, it means\Nthat she really is in love with Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:50.19,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:825063,830193}But why is the renowned lyricist Nohara Jun\Npursuing some oden stand girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:53.90,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:830610,833905}That's not how you\Nshould make the headlines.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:14:00.11,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:833905,840119}It'd be much better if you romanced with me,\Na daughter of a wealthy industrialist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:04.70,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:843206,844707}It's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:13.71,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:849754,853716}She's here!\NLet's hide on the terrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:27.48,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:865186,867480}Are you looking\Nfor someone, Nozomi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:28.64,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:867480,868648}Miki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:30.90,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:868648,870900}I'm sorry, but Fanni isn't coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:32.06,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:870900,872068}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:34.27,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:872068,874279}So it was you\Nwho sent that telegram?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:37.90,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:875863,877907}Ah… Nohara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:43.03,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:877907,883037}Mine-kun, I didn't know that you had\Nsomeone who was so important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.74,0:14:47.37,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:883746,887375}I hate that bastard\Nwho stole your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:48.50,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:887375,888501}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:51.17,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:888501,891170}Knock it off! Hands off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.17,0:14:56.55,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:891170,896551}If you really want to become\Na professional, be quiet and do as I tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.55,0:14:57.55,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:896551,897552}I told you to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.64,0:15:09.77,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:904642,909772}A word of advice, Mine-kun. People who\Nbecome singers quickly lose their shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:13.15,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:909772,913151}I've seen it countless times.\NIt happens to virtually everyone in this business.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:18.03,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:913151,918031}But for some reason I get the impression\Nthat it may be different in your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:22.99,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:920283,922994}This might be the very reason\Nwhy you fascinate me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:29.41,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:922994,929417}I'm sure your beloved Fanni looks to you\Nlike he's the best man in the world right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:32.37,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:929417,932378}but I guarantee that he'll lose\Nhis shine some day as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.37,0:15:36.88,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:932378,936883}If he doesn't, you'd better be aware\Nthat you can't survive in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:41.88,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:938968,941888}Now we've done it, Nohara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:45.89,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:941888,945892}But no matter how hard she tries, there's no way\Nshe can make it to the studio in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:58.69,Default,Taxi driver,0,0,0,,{TIME:954609,958696}20 minutes? That's impossible.\NWe won't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:00.99,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:958696,960990}Please, you have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:02.65,Default,Taxi driver,0,0,0,,{TIME:960990,962658}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:04.86,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:962658,964869}If I don't make it,\Nmy father's medical bills…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:05.82,Default,Taxi driver,0,0,0,,{TIME:964869,965828}Medical bills?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:10.16,Default,Taxi driver,0,0,0,,{TIME:965828,970166}I don't fully know your situation,\Nbut I'll try to do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:15.75,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:972168,975755}{\fad(0,1500)}Aim For The Stars
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:23.80,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:979842,983805}Ahh, I can't wait.\NLet it start already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:27.01,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:983805,987016}Calm down, Kuma-san.\NIt'll start in 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.52,0:16:36.48,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:990520,996484}We warmly welcome our special guests for today:\NIshida Ayumi-san and Master Egawa Isao.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:41.48,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:997443,1001489}What? Mine-kun is missing?\NWhat is she doing? Time is almost up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:46.20,Default,Stuckup,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004367,1006202}Didn't she just quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:48.07,Default,Stuckup,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006202,1008079}She must've been\Ntoo scared to face me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:51.49,Default,Accountant,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008079,1011499}Tch! This is bad. If she doesn't\Nshow up soon, she'll get disqualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:58.21,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015711,1018214}Hurry up! We have to go faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.92,0:17:03.01,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019924,1023010}Three… Two… One…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:04.26,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023428,1024262}Start.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:14.02,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028599,1034021}And now, ladies and gentlemen,\Nhere's what we've all been waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:18.27,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034021,1038276}The final round of the latest season\Nof "Aim For The Stars"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:27.24,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042488,1047243}Ladies and gentlemen, we must also inform you\Nthat unfortunately Mine Nozomi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:31.53,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047243,1051539}the girl who has proved last week\Nto have the best voice, hasn't arrived yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:37.71,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051539,1057712}If she doesn't show up after the challenger's song,\Nshe'll regretfully have to be disqualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:41.00,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057712,1061007}Well, here's the first contestant!\NThis way, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:45.59,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063676,1065595}What's going on?\NWhere is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:48.30,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065595,1068306}Sis, you dummy!\NYou're gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:54.31,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069891,1074312}Don't worry and believe in her.\NI'm sure Nozomi will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.19,0:18:05.32,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080193,1085323}Bravo! It was a splendid interpretation!\NBut let's see what is the opinion of our jury?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:20.08,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096751,1100087}Where in the world is Nozomi-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:23.84,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100588,1103841}47 points!\NOutstanding score!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:29.09,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103841,1109096}As our contestant Mine Nozomi-san hasn't\Nshown up yet, she loses by walkover.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:30.59,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109096,1110598}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112099,1113142}Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:34.85,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113142,1114852}We've been waiting\Nfor you, Nozomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:36.22,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114852,1116229}Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:38.85,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1115853,1118856}{\fad(0,800)}Mine Nozomi's fanclub{NOTE:峰のぞみ後援怪}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.22,0:18:40.73,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116229,1120733}Your uncle is right here!\NYou can't lose, you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:50.49,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124737,1130493}You arrived just in time! If you win\Nthis round, the prize will be yours. Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:05.71,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142046,1145716}{\i1}I can't sing. I've ran all the way here\Nand I'm out of breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:08.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145716,1148970}{\i1}How can I win against her\Nif I'm like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:14.30,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150555,1154308}{\i1}What am I even doing?\NI just have to start singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.18,0:19:20.77,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156185,1160773}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Love, for you and for me  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:愛　あなたと二人}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:25.36,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160773,1165361}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Flowers, for you and for me  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:花　あなたと二人}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:29.86,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165361,1169865}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Faith, for you and for me  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:恋　あなたと二人}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:34.37,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169865,1174370}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Dreams, for you and for me  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:夢　あなたと二人}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.37,0:19:43.87,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174370,1183879}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  The whole world  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  is blessing you and me  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:二人のため　世界はあるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:53.88,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183879,1193889}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  The whole world  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  is blessing you and me  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:二人のため　世界はあるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:20:02.06,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197476,1202064}Good, good, as expected from\Nthe champion. A graceful comeback.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:05.35,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202064,1205359}Will it be the fifth\Nconsecutive victory?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:08.94,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205359,1208946}Let's see what the jury thinks.\NThe judges are ready to press the buttons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.01,0:20:40.81,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238017,1240811}Four judges have given their votes.\NWe now have a score of 40 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:45.94,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240811,1245942}The only remaining vote belongs to Master\NEgawa. It's going to decide everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.94,0:20:48.77,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245942,1248778}How many points\Nis he going to give?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:55.49,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251864,1255493}There it is! 49 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:56.99,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255493,1256994}She wins all the way through!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:20:59.12,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256994,1259121}She becomes the eighth champion\Nin the history of the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:04.54,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259121,1264543}Since the beginning of this edition,\Nshe's received the total of 236 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:06.62,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264543,1266629}What an amazing feat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:01.29,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259372,1261290}{\an8}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:09.88,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1267630,1269882}– Congratulations. Congratulations!\N– Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:12.00,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1270800,1272009}– She did it!\N– She did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:14.38,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1272009,1274387}– Sis did it, Mom!\N– She won!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:25.85,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281811,1285856}The champion has been crowned\Nand now gets the grand prize of 200,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:33.03,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1288985,1293030}So, Mine-san, how are you\Ngoing to use this money?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:36.28,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293030,1296283}With this, I'll be finally able to pay\Nmy father's hospitalization expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.28,0:21:38.32,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296283,1298327}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.11,0:21:45.33,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1297118,1305334}{\fad(2000,3500)}Award{NOTE:賞}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.55,0:21:55.92,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1313551,1315928}Mr. Egawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.76,0:22:00.14,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316762,1320141}I've been waiting for you.\NI wanted to congratulate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:02.51,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320141,1322518}Thank you very much, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.51,0:22:03.60,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322518,1323602}Thanks to you, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.60,0:22:07.89,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1323602,1327898}That's not it. You owe your victory\Nto yourself and your talent only.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.89,0:22:10.15,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327898,1330151}To be honest, it was…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.65,0:22:16.53,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331652,1336532}It was very difficult for me to judge you\Nafter I had kicked you out of my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.53,0:22:18.78,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1336532,1338784}Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.78,0:22:20.41,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1338784,1340411}I feel proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.41,0:22:25.33,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1340411,1345332}After you've gone, you must've suffered a lot,\Nyet you've quickly improved so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.45,0:22:27.46,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1346459,1347460}Sir…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.46,0:22:29.50,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1347460,1349503}You don't have to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.50,0:22:32.33,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1349503,1352339}I can only imagine everything\Nyou've been through.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.33,0:22:37.72,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1352339,1357720}I'm well aware how hard you\Nmust've worked in order to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:42.89,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1357720,1362892}Despite that, I closed my heart to you\Nand just kept watching in silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.89,0:22:47.93,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1362892,1367938}Only the ones that can endure\Nsuch trial can become real singers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.93,0:22:50.23,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1367938,1370232}You passed this trial\Nwith flying colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:52.35,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1370232,1372359}You…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.52,0:22:55.86,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1373527,1375863}You lived up to my expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.07,0:22:58.69,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1377073,1378699}What do you think, Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:01.28,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1378699,1381285}Would you agree to live\Nat my place one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:02.87,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1381285,1382870}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:04.87,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1383829,1384872}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.41,0:23:09.79,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1385414,1389794}Sir… I will never leave you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.79,0:23:11.33,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1389794,1391337}No matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.46,0:23:16.00,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1393464,1396008}I'll follow you anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:18.01,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1396008,1398010}Very well.
Comment: 0,0:23:22.64,0:23:22.64,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1402648,1402648}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.59,0:23:29.64,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1403599,1409647}{\i1}Nozomi is overjoyed at the news that she can\Nreceive lessons under Egawa Isao again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.64,0:23:32.52,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1409647,1412525}{\i1}However, as if blind\Nto Nozomi's feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.52,0:23:37.65,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1412525,1417655}{\i1}Egawa Isao focuses on teaching Miki,\Nwho is going to make her debut soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.65,0:23:42.24,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1417655,1422243}{\i1}Day after day, Nozomi becomes\Nmore and more anxious and impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.24,0:23:47.83,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1422243,1427832}{\i1}Then she hears Egawa Isao cold words:\N"I don't feel like giving lessons to you".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.83,0:23:52.62,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1427832,1432628}{\i1}Please look forward to the next episode:\N"Singing in the sunset".
